{
  "stem": "769.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Three sisters.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well in the beginning from the war, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it's very panic, a very big panic.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, when they came in, they started right away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have to tell you a short story, which is very interesting.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I was--when I was in jail, I know my friend, the same age from me, he was a communist.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he, every Saturday, come to us just for eat fish, Jewish fish.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He so love it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Fresh halibut.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My mother bake it, and Jewish fish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He always loved it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were the best friends.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "When the war break out, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he-- I didn't know where he is, because we look out for ourselves, everybody for ourselves.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] A few days later, I find out he, in the communist-- he is in the Hitler Youth.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was a German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He wore the red band with the Hakenkreuz, and looking for communist.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He looked for me, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he came to us in-- I was not home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I was by an uncle-- they call this in Lodz the ballot.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "This is the-- the-- a section where was the ghetto was after that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I had an uncle there, and I was by him, hiding out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I came home, and I decided to run away because after when they took us to the police station to clean, and they beat me up and I got-- damaged my ear, then I decided to run away to Russia.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Now the thing is, what I told you, one guy in the jail, but I give him the whole food when I'm sitting there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he is a delegate to the [INAUDIBLE] industry to the Communist Party.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
